				<pubDate>Sat, 29 Apr 2017 20:53:59 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>OZ Ouroboros</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1743859</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;So,&nbsp;I&nbsp;wrote&nbsp;a&nbsp;song...</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;I&nbsp;REGRET&nbsp;NOTHING</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Splish splash splish splash splish splash splish<br /> BANANAFISH<br /> Splish splash splish splash splish splash splish<br /> BANANAFISH~</p> <p>I've got this feeling<br /> Una-peel-ing</p> <p>That it will mutate further and bring (BRING~)</p> <p>Death death death death death death death<br /> BANANAFISH<br /> Mess mess mess mess mess mess mess<br /> MONANAFISH</p> <p>It chomps and crunches<br /> I've got my hunches<br /> It's a brute! Smells like fruit!</p> <p>Strap it in, trap it in, what-the-hell-is-happenin'?</p> <p>Splish splash splish splash splish splash splish<br /> BANANAFISH (BOOP BOOP A DOOP A DOOP)<br /> Crish crash crish crash crish crash crish<br /> CABANAFISH</p> <p>I've got no answer<br /> This thing poops cancer<br /> This strange, hellish, BANANA-LIKE FIIIISH</p> <p>Don't need drugs, to know its kind<br /> Just screws with all our minds!<br /> It needs bananas, and some meat,<br /> At every feeding time!</p> <p>It ate a gator, it ate my cat!<br /> It ate a D-Class, how 'bout that?<br /> It ate a shark, I'll have you know,<br /> That Bananafish just wants to grow, grow, grow, grow&#8230;</p> <p>Splish splash splish splash splish splash splish<br /> BANANAFISH (BOOP BOOP A DOOP A DOOP)<br /> Gnish gnash gnish gnash gnish gnash gnish<br /> GONANAFISH</p> <p>It's a real life gator, and birdnanafish<br /> A sharky, and kitty, and dognanafish<br /> A snakeyfish and a&#8230; personfish too! (Oh, yeah!)</p> <p>This strange, hellish<br /> BANANA-LIKE FIIIIISH</p> <p>Bananafish (Splish, splash, splish) (It's a fish with a peel!)</p> <p>Bananafish (Splish, splash, splish) (Now you can have a banana that eats you too!)</p> <p>Bananafish (Splish, splash, splish) (This fish drives me BANANAS)</p> <p>Bananafish (Splish, splash, splish)</p> <p>BOOP A DOOP A DOOP DOOP BOOP</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
