				<wikidot:authorName>sirpudding</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>348648</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Piscine is Latin for fish-like, and is clearly the context meant here.</p> <p>Although biologically &quot;fish&quot; is parapheletic, because the organisms we call fish contain groups distantly enough related to each other that they share a least common ancestor with all vertebrates.</p> 
				 	]]>
