"http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1492899585" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" >Zyn</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1492899585" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" >Jacob Conwell</a></span> for looking this over! As always, you guys are awesome. ^^</p> 
